            <commentid>201</commentid>
            <who name="Sebastian Werner">info</who>
            <bug_when>2006-07-11 18:25:22 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>For example instead of code like this:

  if (this._currentPreview)
  {
    this._currentPreview.dispose();
    this._currentPreview = null;
  }

  if (this._selectorButton)
  {
    this._selectorButton.dispose();
    this._selectorButton = null;
  }

We could write:

  this._disposeObjectFields(&quot;_currentPreview&quot;, &quot;_selectorButton&quot;, ...);</thetext>
